    "Equation 7 demands for n i 1 × ⋯ × n i N nodes, which indi- cates an exponential rate of computational cost growth with the number of dimensions.",
    "Adaptive stochastic collocation targets the reduction of this computational effort through an adaptive sparse grid of collocation points: the objective is to wisely place more points of the grid in the important directions to prioritize the collection of highly informative data.",
